data.description: Price Adjustment and includes 1 Year HMS Home Warranty for buyer(s) piece of mind.  SELLER HAS A VA ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE!  Seller's mortgage rate is 2.625%. You do not have to be a Veteran to assume this mortgage.  Opportunity awaits buyers buying for primary residence.  “SOLD,” is definitely what you’ll say when you see this TWO YEAR YOUNG 3/2/2 home with hurricane windows, tile throughout, whole house generator, and extra-large shed.  Perfectly positioned on a 10,000 sq ft lot this home is conveniently located to beaches, interstate 75, fine dining, and Wellen Park.  Stone enhancements on the exterior draw your eyes in upon arrival.  A concrete drive and walkway are the guides to the etched glass front entry. Open the door to view the soaring cathedral ceilings that grace the main living area where you’ll gather with family and friends.  The adjacent kitchen includes stately wood cabinets, granite counters, tiled backsplash, and stainless appliances. The eating area is flooded with light from the slider that leads to the covered lanai. A split floorplan finds the Owner’s suite to the right and includes dual walk-in closets, step-in shower, granite top vanity and linen closet. The second and third bedrooms have double closets and share the second bathroom with glass-enclosed tub/shower combo and granite-topped vanity.  A separate laundry room has a sink and storage shelf and will be your drop area when entering from the garage. The outdoor area is quite private and has enough room to add a pool if so desired.  Undoubtedly the substantial shed will be well used thus allowing the two-car garage to house vehicles only. This home is a true gem and is priced to sell. NEW A/C OCTOBER 2022. NEW WHOLEHOUSE GENERATOR OCTOBER 2022. Propane tank has a 500 gallon capacity.  Call today for your private showing.
